N = int(input())
A = [int(i) for i in input().split()]

for i in range(N):
    print(A.index(i + 1) + 1, end=' ')



def main():
    n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a = list(enumerate(a, 1))
    a = sorted(a, key=lambda x: x[1])
    a = [str(i[0]) for i in a]
    print('\n'.join(a))


if __name__ == '__main__':
    main()
